{"product_id":"hej-organic-sun-drops-15ml","title":"HEJ Organic Sun Drops 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSun Drops tan your skin evenly and ensure a glowy finish. Aloe vera provides your skin with intensive moisture, can be combined with all care products.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGentle tanning effect thanks to DHA\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAloe Vera nourishes the skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCan be dosed individually\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% fragrance free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003ePeel your skin before use for an even result. Mix 2-5 drops into the care product and distribute it evenly over the face, neck and décolleté. Wash your hands after use. The tanning starts after approx. 5-8 hours and lasts for 3-5 days. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (Water), Dihydroxyacetone, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Pentylene Glycol, Xanthan Gum, Citric Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905824362823,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-sun-drops-15ml-961268.png?v=1739897167","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hej-organic-sun-drops-15ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}